      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some visible clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor door dings, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will soon require new brake pads and a suspension refresh to restore its original handling. It is a solid, honest car for someone who doesn't mind a few cosmetic flaws in exchange for a lower price point.",
