    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, offering a comfortable and dependable driving experience. While the interior is clean and the mechanical components are sound, there are some minor cosmetic imperfections such as small scratches and light interior wear consistent with its age. Overall, it is a solid, well-cared-for vehicle ready for its next owner.",
