    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S in impeccable condition. This example retains its numbers-matching 13B-REW power plant, featuring a perfectly synchronized sequential twin-turbocharger system. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the engine exhibits superb compression across all rotor faces, and the five-speed manual transmission provides crisp, positive engagement. The chassis benefits from a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring neutral handling and high-speed stability. With a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation and a meticulously maintained cooling system to mitigate heat soak, this FD represents the pinnacle of 90s analog performance. Turn-key and ready for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
