      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, mirror-like gloss, the exterior is free of even the smallest stone chips or swirls, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin retains that signature new-car scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and a recent multi-point inspection from a certified specialist. With exceptionally low mileage and a meticulously clean undercarriage, the driving experience is tight, responsive, and completely silent. No accidents, no modifications, and no stories\u2014just a flawless example for the discerning enthusiast who demands the best.",
